title: 2021 New York City mayoral election
added: On September 9th, 2021, A [[POLITICO]] news article revealed Former Democratic Primary Candidate [[Andrew Yang]]'s plans to leave the Democratic Party and form a new political party. It was also confirmed that he will resume his run for [[Mayor of New York City]] under the newly formed Third Party, scheduled to be founded on October 5th, 2021, along with a new book Yang is releasing. The name of the new party is unknown currently.>{{cite news |last1=Thompson |first1=Alex |title=Andrew Yang to launch a third party |url=https://www.politico.com/amp/news/2021/09/09/andrew-yang-third-party-511033|access-date=16 September 2021 |work=[[POLITICO]] |date=9 September 2021}}</ref>
